sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-header', templateUrl: './header.component.html', styleUrls: ['./header.component.scss'] }) export class HeaderComponent { constructor(private router:Router){} createPost(){ this.router.navigate(['create-post']) } gotoProfile(){ this.router.navigate } }
